        <p><b>Assalamu Alaikum,</b></p>
        <p>It is my honor and privilege to welcome you to <b>Saidpur Residential Model School (SRMS)</b>, an institution devoted to nurturing discipline, morality, and quality education. Since its inception, SRMS has been committed to establishing a safe, student-friendly, and academically enriched environment where every learner can grow with confidence.</p>
