        <p>At SRMS, we provide Residential, Non-Residential, Day-Care, and Night-Care facilities to support students from various backgrounds. With trained teachers, updated teaching methods, strict discipline, and personalized guidance, we ensure that every student receives the attention they need to reach their full potential.</p>
        <p>I warmly invite all parents and guardians to work together with us in guiding the next generation toward a brighter, more successful future.</p>
        <p>Thank you for your trust and continuous support.</p>
